00:56:37,290 --> 00:56:40,260


591
00:56:40,460 --> 00:56:42,090


592
00:56:41,064 --> 00:56:42,862
被活組織包著的
Surrounded by living tissue.

593
00:56:42,862 --> 00:56:43,483
對，是的
Oh, right.

594
00:56:42,300 --> 00:56:43,730


595
00:56:44,276 --> 00:56:47,029
