Shut up!

617
00:57:24,232 --> 00:57:26,860
你還是不明白，對不對？
You still don't get it, do you?

618
00:57:27,027 --> 00:57:28,518
他會找到她的
He'll find her.

619
00:57:28,518 --> 00:57:30,406
他就是要那樣做
That's what he does.

620
00:57:30,406 --> 00:57:32,115
他只會那樣做
That's all he does.

